               <msContents>
                  <summary/>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <title type="incomplete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3165Menas">ገድል፡ ወስምዕ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡ ሚናስ፡
                    መስተጋድል፡ ሰማዕቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሚናስ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚናስ፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ግብጽ፡ እንተ፡ ስማ፡ ቄጥባ፡ በስሙ፡ ለመኰንን፡ ዘሐነጸ፡
                    ውስቴታ፡ ማኅፈደ፡ ወአጽንዓ፡ አረፋቲሃ። ወስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚናስ፡ አውዶክሲስ፡</incipit>
                    <note>There are several lacunae in the middle of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="22r"/>
                     <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2386Taamme">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
              አመ፡ ፲ወ፭፡ እምነ፡ ስኔ፡ በዓሉ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚናስ፡ ወቅዳሴ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፤ ቀዳሚሃ፡ ለመንክራቲሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ሚናስ፡
              ዘኅንፀተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፤ ወበእንተ፡ ሰሚዐ፡ ገድሉ፡ ብሂሎ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ትዮፍሎስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘሀገር፡ ዐባይ፡ እለ፡ እስክንድርያ።
             </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez"> ቀዳሚት፡ መንክራቲሁ። ወሀሎ፡ ብእሲ፡ ባዕለ፡ አግማል፡ ወሀለወት፡ ሎቱ፡ ነቅይት፡ <supplied reason="explanation" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe" xml:lang="ar">ناقة</supplied>ይእቲ፡ ወመካን፡</incipit>
                     <note>Cp. the Sǝnkǝsār entry for the 15th Sǝne and
               <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MSUZBPZK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Surius1618November"/><title level="m">De probatis sanctorum vitis quas tam ex Mss. Codicibus, quam ex editis authoribus R. P. F. Laurentius Surius carthusiae coloniensis professus primum editit &amp; in duodecim menses distribuit. November</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Laurentius</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Surius</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Coloniae Agrippinae</pubPlace><publisher>Sumptibus Ioannis Kreps &amp; Hermanni Mylij</publisher><date>1618</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_VZkrY2lu4dsC</note><citedRange unit="page">241–246</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                  </msItem>

